Description:
After a tough fight, you finished off Tulah, the spider queen.

Now you will take a short break to regain strength and will look for a way to get out of the cave, also you need some time for the effects of the Tulah poison to wear off little by little.
DescriptionAction: While you wait, you can open the cocoons of the dead adventurers captured by Tulah and search for useful items.
